function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
--Stana calls out Torben
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CON_BARK_STANA01, ID_STANA_NPC)
--Torben moves to Stana, delete Follower
	followerTorben = Hydra.QuestGetFollowers()[1]
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerTorben) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerTorben, false)
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerTorben)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerTorben, LOC_TORBEN_01, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerTorben, LOC_TORBEN_01)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerTorben)
		Hydra.ActorDelete(followerTorben)
	end	
--Enable static Torben
	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_TORBEN_01)
--Progress Scene
	Hydra.EventSend("ConfrontStana")
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

--Enable Boss Fight
	--Stana Static
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(LOC_STANA_NPC, EFF_VANISH)
		Hydra.ActorDisable(ID_STANA_NPC)
	--Stana Boss
		Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_STANA_BOSS)
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(LOC_STANA_BOSS, EFF_VANISH)
	--Guards
		tGuards = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_STANA_NPC, "Guards")
		for i, idGuard in ipairs(tGuards) do
			Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idGuard, true)
			Hydra.ActorSetNoDamage(idGuard, false)
			Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idGuard, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_0)
		end
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

--Stana Combatant Disappear, turn to static Stana
	Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idActorKilled, true)
	Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroup(idActorKilled, EFF_VANISH)
--Enable Wounded NPC Stana
	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_STANA_WOUNDED)
	Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroup(LOC_STANA_NPC, EFF_VANISH)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_STANA_WOUNDED, EFF_VANISH)


end
